        <head>Sunshine</head>
        <lg Chorus="yes" number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>We've shared this land forever </l>
          <l>But we've never looked around </l>
          <l>To see </l>
          <l>We co-exist for years </l>
          <l>We're desert people </l>
          <l>We are trees </l>
          <l>We talk love to each other </l>
          <l>Common interest </l>
          <l>Common fears </l>
          <l>Respecting ourselves </l>
          <l>Respecting our lands </l>
          <l>Respecting our self-destruction </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>We should be lying in the sunshine </l>
          <l>together </l>
